        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">West Coast Beaches</h2>
        <p>Along the western coast of Ibiza you'll find two more amazing beaches which can easily be reached via car or public transportation from Ibiza Town.</p>
        <p>A bit west of Sant Antoni de Portmany is the popular <strong>Platja de Comte</strong> beach, which is known for its radiant light blue waters and beautiful scenery. This beach overlooks the wide Illa des Bosc island, which is only about 2,000 feet (600 m) off the coast.</p>
